{"tid":956474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方刑事及保安處長李志恒北海道遇車禍　無綫消息：對頭車內是曾志偉","createTime":"2018-12-26T09:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T13:06:22.000Z","uid":20419,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3d96dbeb55eef94c025470bd5e88dcc6504817e0","tid":956474,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/3E30Rr?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F3E30Rr%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=MVClInYvP9WegFKTBMkVBAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a1eb9991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/3E30Rr?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n多間傳媒今日引述消息指，警務處刑事及保安處處長李志恒昨日與家人在日本遇車禍受傷，頸部受傷但無生命危險。無綫新聞另引述消息指，涉事對頭車內的是藝人曾志偉。<br />\n綜合各香港媒體消息，李志恒是在昨日與家人於北海道小樽旅遊時，遇上嚴重車禍。李志恒頸椎受傷，傷勢頗重，他目前已完成手術，並無生命危險。<br />\n無綫新聞報道指，李志恒在日本北海道遇車禍受傷，對頭車內是藝人曾志偉，但報道未有交代曾志偉的情況。<br />\n李志恒先生於1988年加入香港警務處，任職督察。他於2015年初調任保安部擔任部門副主管，並於同年六月擢升為警務處助理處長，掌管保安部。2018年初擢升為刑事及保安處處長。<br />\n相關報道：蘋果日報／無綫新聞／香港01／商業電台"},{"pid":"c2e40919b2f789b3cea63c54681df04ab237fda6","tid":956474,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03fdbd587a764f527022e228effa48f764ac509","tid":956474,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"境外車禍應該告唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c3879bd0148aee8338fd3fc39a2f6caea87e42","tid":956474,"uid":35021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"膠棟：阿頭大鑊啦，李Sir出咗事！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WcsFKAf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWcsFKAf.png&h=0dc2a98c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f06c65fccbdc4623f8b2e1a2ec17b6a63708b966","tid":956474,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,